reviewText:
Good day all

Definitely a must have! Exceptional coaching techniques , coupled with informative clips from great past and present West Indian Cricketers. My son and i sat down and watched it together after the launch in Trincity Mall and it surely lived up to my expectations and more! Kudos to Daren and his team on this compilation! Ensure you have a copy cause it can make the difference in your budding cricket career!
